│ violate those flags, the transformed operation may\n    // produce poison   │
│ when the original code would not.\n    // Avoid the folding if the false    │
│ value might be a NaN or violate ninf/nnan.\n    if                          │
│ (isa<FPMathOperator>(TVI)) {\n      // Check for NaN issues using the       │
